DNS CHANGER is a free open-source utility for Windows that allows users to quickly switch between different DNS providers, test DNS performance, and manage network settings. Packaged as a portable RAR archive with no installation required.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

