🚀 QUICK START

1. Download the RAR file from the link above
2. Extract using WinRAR, 7-Zip, or any RAR extractor
3. Right-click on .exe → Run as Administrator
4. Select your DNS preset or enter custom servers
5. Click "Apply DNS" and enjoy faster browsing

No installation required - completely portable!

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

✨ KEY FEATURES

• One-click DNS switching between 12+ providers (Google, Cloudflare, OpenDNS, Quad9, AdGuard)
• Custom DNS entry support with IPv4 and IPv6
• Multi-adapter management (Wi-Fi, Ethernet, Virtual)
• DNS performance benchmarking with real-time response testing
• DNS cache viewer and one-click flusher
• Network diagnostics and connection testing
• Portable - runs from USB, no registry changes
• Full open-source code included in the RAR

