🔧 HOW TO USE

Step 1: Extract the RAR archive to any folder
Step 2: .exe as Administrator
Step 3: Select your network adapter from the list
Step 4: Choose a DNS preset or enter custom IPs
Step 5: Click "Apply DNS" to change settings
Step 6: Use "Test Connection" to verify functionality
Step 7: Click "Flush Cache" for immediate effect

All settings are saved automatically in the config files.

