📄 README.TXT (extracted from RAR)

==================================================
DNS CHANGER v2.1.0 - Open Source
==================================================

Thank you for downloading DNS Changer!

This tool allows you to:
- Change DNS servers with one click
- Test DNS response times
- Manage multiple network adapters
- Flush DNS cache instantly

HOW TO RUN:
1. Extract all files from the RAR archive
2. Right-click .exe → Run as Administrator
3. The GUI will launch - select your DNS and apply

TROUBLESHOOTING:
- If DNS doesn't change, run as Administrator
- For Windows 11, disable "Randomized MAC addresses" temporarily
- Check Windows Firewall if connection drops

LICENSE: MIT (Open Source)
VERSION: 2.1.0
RELEASE DATE: March 2025

For source code, see the /source folder included.

==================================================

