v2.1.0 (March 2026)
────────────────────
• Added IPv6 DNS support
• New performance benchmark tool
• Added 4 new DNS providers (AdGuard, CleanBrowsing, Alternate, Verisign)
• Improved Windows 11 compatibility
• Fixed adapter detection bug

